name: The Vindication I
description:
Yesterday on 9/10/2021 I finally earned my first “Visual Storyteller” badge on FB thanks to the fine folks at weirdbook. This is after 10 years of being on groups and posting lotta OC under main name the Black Iron Kisses banner. The badges arroved for both Vash and Main simultaneously.

 I think I used to have “conversation starter” over 6 years ago  but not sure if that was for groups. Anyway, as thanks and documentation into my paranoia over all of this i’m making this visual post as an NFT commemoration, of 1000 editions available less than $0.23 value on the HicEtNunc NFT marketplace (Link in comments) . If you have further questions please feel free to reach out further. via DM or comments and lets set a time to talk about it.
